OL,5, Former US intelligence contractor      
OL,6, Edward Snowden, who leaked extensive US
OL,7, intelligence surveillance operations,  
OL,8, has been granted Russian citizenship.  
OL,10,FThe decree was signed by Russian       
OL,11,FPresident Vladimir Putin on Monday.    
OL,13,FMr Snowden, 39, has been living in     
OL,14,Fexile in Russia since exposing the     
OL,15,FNational Security Agency (NSA)         
OL,16,Fprogramme affecting millions of        
OL,17,FAmericans in 2013.                     
OL,19,FMr Snowden, who faces espionage charges
OL,20,Fin the US, has made no public comments.
